cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about generating keyphrases for a document, which is a task related to natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence, suggesting that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG), making cs.IR and cs.LG likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper proposes a new evaluation method that incorporates knowledge from a knowledge base, which is related to neural networks (NE), making cs.NE a possible sub-category.
